{
  "texts": [
    "But despite having been able to uncover this statistic, there is a crucial piece of information that has been omitted: the overall availability of the underground water supplying Cerrillos.",
    "This lack of information, which could have vital consequences for the everyday life of residents, was strategically mobilised by MOSACAT:",
    "'Imagine that they will come to deliver water to you on a water truck'.",
    "And that is shocking for anyone … So I would tell them: 'They will cut the water so that a company can keep operating.",
    "They will cut our water, imagine, from 3 to 4 in the afternoon'."
  ]
}